text: Micatocomus petalacmoides is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 1988. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Micatocomus petalacmoides. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Calliini Category:Beetles described in 1988
